     H            Y.
     F** UTLR81 *******************************************************
     F*  RETRIEVE USER ID AND MAIL ADDRESS                            *
     F*  J.WATANABE    2021.06.28                                     *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR81'
     F*                    PARM           $USER  10
     F*                    PARM           $ADDR  30
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*   IN  $USER : 10A USER ID (IF BLANK, USE SDS USER)
     F*   OUT $ADDR : 30A MAIL ADDRESS
     F*       $RTN  :  1A RETURN (BLANK=OK, *=ERROR)
     F*****************************************************************
     FRGAPP01 IF  E           K        DISK
     E                    ERR     1   1 30
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                      254 263 #USER
     C*---------------------------------------------------------------*
     C* PARAMETER
     C*---------------------------------------------------------------*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $USER  10
     C                     PARM           $ADDR  30
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
     C*---------------------------------------------------------------*
     C* MAIN ROUTINE
     C*---------------------------------------------------------------*
      *
     C           $USER     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVEL#USER     @USER  10
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL$USER     @USER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           @USER     CHAINRGAPP01              99
      *
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELR1ADDR    $ADDR     P
     C                     MOVE ' '       $RTN
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELERR,1     $ADDR
     C                     MOVE '*'       $RTN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
** ERR
